~ start
Jester: riddle?
Decide.
- yes
	set GameController.state.node = "JesterCrying"
	set GameController.state.level = "1"
	Jester: riddle.
	- option a
		Jester: that is correct!
		set GameController.state.event = "riddle_won"
	- option b
		Jester: that is incorrect!
		set GameController.state.event = "riddle_lose"
- no
	Jester: fine then
=> END

~ win
Jester: you have bested me
=> END

~ lose
Jester: you have not bested me
=> END